      <guid>https://www.linuxreader.com/ansible/archive/practice-exam/</guid>
      <description>Tasks 1-2: Configuration and adhoc commands These tasks are all about setting up inventory, ansible.cfg, and access to hosts. There were a few things I needed to search documentation for.&#xA;Inventory I ended up opening the official inventory page to make sure this was done right.</description>
